Fourth Department,

May, 1956

(May 2, 1956) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Gerard Dennis, Appellant, against Robert E. Murphy, as Warden of Auburn Prison, Respondent.

Order affirmed, without costs of this appeal to either party. All concur. (Appeal from an order of Cayuga Special Term dismissing the writ of habeas corpus and remanding relator to the custody of the Warden of Auburn Prison.) Present — McCurn, P. J., Vaughan, Kimball, Williams and Bastow, JJ.
